  <brief_title>Evaluation of a Ionic Silver and Honey Preparation to Treat Chronic Wounds of the Lower Legs</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Label Study (Phase 2) to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerance and Efficacy of a Ionic Silver and Honey Preparation to Treat Chronic Wounds of the Lower Legs</official_title>
